        </ul>

        <h3>Session Cookies</h3>

        <p>Session cookies are those that exist the time the user is browsing the webpage and are deleted at the
            end.</p>


        <h3>Persistent Cookies</h3>

        <p>These cookies are stored on the user's terminal for a longer period, simplifying the control of the preferences chosen without having to repeat certain parameters on every visit to the website.
